Third-party test data vendored in this repository
-------------------------------------------------

Crystallography Open Database (COD), https://www.crystallography.net/cod/

  Entries from the COD are vendored verbatim under tests/wild/cod/ as the
  project's real-world CIF corpus. All data in the COD have been placed in
  the public domain by their contributors; the entries here are used under
  the CC0 1.0 Universal public-domain dedication. Each entry records its
  COD number and source URL in its manifest.yaml, and the per-entry list
  is generated into tests/golden/ATTRIBUTIONS.md.

  CC0 imposes no attribution requirement. The entries are listed anyway,
  because a public-domain dedication does not make provenance optional:
  a reader must be able to trace any file in this repository back to the
  record it came from.
